kilobits per second. This latest ingredient in the
telecommunications alphabet soup should provide more substantial
nourishment. &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; (EDITOR'S NOTE: Herb Brody is a senior editor of ``Technology
Review.'') &LR;  &QL; 
