<HEADLINE>
JASON PATRIC PUTS HIMSELF IN A NAUGHTY NEW ROLE
</HEADLINE>
  1000 words, with color slides and black and white photos of Jason
Patric available)
 By IVOR DAVIS 
 World rights except Great Britain and Australia 
 Distributed by New York Times Special Features)  
<TEXT>
<P>
   He's a cold, sexual athlete in his latest film, ``Your Friends
and Neighbors.'' And it's a role that Jason Patric, who also
produced the film, carefully picked for himself.
</P>
<P>
   Slugged:  &UR; BC-IVOR-JASON-PATRIC-ART-NYTSF, priority code r,
category code e.
</P>
