MEDICAL BREAKTHROUGHS YOU CAN TOUCH (WITH ART) 
 KIDS WHO CAN'T SAY GOODBYE 
 MAKE YOUR SHOPPING 'ROBOT' SEARCH THE NET
</HEADLINE>
  (Eds.: Innoventions is cq.)  
<TEXT>
<P>
   These articles (described in more detail below) are free to
LifeBeat clients. They can be purchased individually by non-clients
by contacting Connie White at (800) 444-0267 or (816) 822-8448, or
by fax at (816) 822-1444; she also has information on how to
subscribe to LifeBeat.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; PLEASE NOTE: &LR;  The pictures that accompany these stories are
