</P>
<P>
   &UR; MEDICAL BREAKTHROUGHS YOU CAN TOUCH &QL; 
 &UR; (700 words. Includes color slides of Innoventions hall and mascot
Tom Morrow.) &QL; 
 &UR; By KATHY SENA &QL; 
 &UR; From California Health magazine &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   The health-and-fitness world of the future is now on display in
Disneyland's new ``Innoventions'' exhibit. We're talking hands-on
fun here, for grown-ups and kids. The exhibit combines Disney's
storytelling abilities with the expertise of companies like Kaiser
Permanent to demonstrate the hottest developments in technology.
</P>
<P>
   Slugged BC-FUTURE-OF-HEALTH-LIFEBEAT-ART-NYTSF, priority code r,
category code l) &QL;
