<P>
   Some children have difficulty with transitions because they
think that all their fun is being removed _ and that they'll never
have a good time again. Sound advice on what to day and do to help
children move along.
</P>
<P>
   (slugged: BC-SAY-GOODBYE-LIFEBEAT-NYTSF, priority code r,
