</TRAILER>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19980824.0158 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-24 11:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8930 &Cx1f; tab-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-DAYTIME-DIVA-PROFILE-     08-24 0448
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-DAYTIME-DIVA-PROFILE-AND-MORE-NYTSF </SLUG>
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   LEEZA GIBBONS: DAYTIME DIVA
</P>
