<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-24 13:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9068 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BBN-McGWIRE-HNS &LR;      08-24 1310
