<HEADLINE>
NINA SIMONE BRINGS ELEGANCE AND ANGER TO HER PERFORMANE 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By ROBERTA PENN  
 c.1998 Seattle Post-Intelligencer  
<TEXT>
<P>
   SEATTLE _ It is a rare sight in the '90s, a 65-year-old woman
dressed in a glittering evening gown with her fist raised in the
black-power salute. Few people could pull off such a seemingly
mixed statement before a crowd of 3,000 and not be laughed off the
