Tuesday, Aug. 25, and thereafter. If you have any questions, please
call Tina May at (206) 448-8355.
</P>
<P>
   INTERVIEW-JENKINS (Seattle) Interview with Tamara Jenkins,
director/writer of the film, ``Slums of Beverly Hills,'' which
opens Friday.
</P>
<P>
   By Paula Nechak. (story will move in the ``e'' category)
</P>
<P>
   BARD-BROADWAY (New York) The Bard on Broadway: a look at
Shakespeare in New York this summer, including Helen Hunt on the
boards and other highlights.
</P>
<P>
   By Jeffrey Eric Jenkins. (story will move in the ``e'' category)
</P>
<P>
   NINA-SIMONE (Seattle) It is a rare sight in the '90s, a
65-year-old woman dressed in a glittering evening gown with her
