   BE FIRM: Experts say that in an effort to be kind and gentle,
too many women give their stalkers mixed signals, leaving them with
the belief that if they keep at it they will eventually win the
women they desire.
</P>
<P>
   In his book ``The Gift of Fear'' (Little, Brown, $22.95,
paperback), Gavin de Becker says that ``a rejection based on any
condition, say, that she wants to move to another city, just gives
him something to challenge.'' He suggests that women should ``never
