class of 25 astronauts, including Idaho teacher Barbara Morgan, who
backed up Christa McAuliffe on the ill-fated Challenger mission in
1986. By MARK CARREAU.
</P>
<P>
   TEXAS-FLOODING (Undated) _ At least 16 people die in flooding in
the border town of Del Rio as remnants of Tropical Storm Charley
pounded the border city and neighboring Ciudad Acuna, Mexico,
leaving some 20 missing, officials said. By THADDEUS HERRICK and
JAMES PINKERTON.
</P>
