   BUSINESS/FINANCIAL NEWS (``f'' category)
</P>
<P>
   ACCELERNET-INTERNET (Houston) _ A company is reportedly the
first in the country to use a UHF television frequency to deliver
wireless Internet service. AccelerNet claims it can deliver
information at lightening speeds, though a regular phone line is
required to upload information. By DWIGHT SILVERMAN.
</P>
