<P>
   BBA-MARINERS-FASHION (SEasttle) The Mariners are not winning,
but they might lead the major leagues in fashion. They seem to play
in a different-looking uniform each day. How many do they have? How
do they choose which one to wear? Are they superstitious or keep
track of how many wins they have in each?
</P>
<P>
   By Jim Street. (story will move in the ``s'' category)
