<P>
   FORECASTERS-FLOODING (Undated) _ ``Core rains'' can become
death-dealing storm systems awesome in their destructiveness, as
with the system that hit Del Rio, Texas. ``During the daytime they
may cover an area of 15 counties,'' one meteorologist says. ``At
night they collapse and intensify _ maybe they cover three or four
counties. They collapse just like a black hole.'' By ALLAN TURNER.
</P>
