<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-24 21:04 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9954 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-PAGING-INTE     08-24 0032
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-PAGING-INTERACTIVE-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
ATTN EDITORS:  

</HEADLINE>
